# Portfolio Project Rules

## Design System — Nature-Inspired Editorial

Use ONLY these colors. Never use the old blue `#2563EB`.

| Token | Value | Use |
|-------|-------|-----|
| Background | `#0D1A0F` | Page background |
| Surface | `#162418` | Cards, inputs, mobile nav |
| Accent green | `#4A7C59` | Primary buttons, completed dots, progress bars |
| Gold | `#C9A84C` | Logo dot, eyebrow labels, ornaments, gold buttons |
| Text primary | `#F0EBE0` | Headings, labels |
| Text secondary | `#9A9080` | Body copy, placeholders |
| Border | `rgba(201,168,76,0.10)` | Default borders |
| Border hover | `rgba(201,168,76,0.25)` | Hover/focus borders |

## Typography Rules

- Display headings: Playfair Display via `style={{ fontFamily: "var(--font-display, Playfair Display, serif)" }}` + add `italic` Tailwind class
- Section eyebrows (labels above headings): `text-xs font-medium text-[#C9A84C] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]`
- Body copy: `text-[#9A9080] leading-[1.85]`

## Animation Pattern

All scroll-triggered animations must use:
```tsx
const ref = useRef(null);
const inView = useInView(ref, { once: true, margin: "-60px" });
// Then: animate={inView ? { opacity: 1, y: 0 } : {}}
```

## Icon Rules

`lucide-react` does NOT export `Github` or `Linkedin`. Always import from:
```tsx
import { GithubIcon, LinkedinIcon } from "@/components/ui/SocialIcons";
```

## Content Rules

All content (projects, skills, timeline data) lives in `src/data/`. Never hardcode content in components.

## Component Imports

```tsx
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/Button";    // variants: primary, outline, ghost, gold
import { Card } from "@/components/ui/Card";         // prop: glow={true} for hover effect
import { Badge } from "@/components/ui/Badge";       // variants: accent, muted, gold
import { ProgressBar } from "@/components/ui/ProgressBar"; // animated on scroll
```
